{"ts":"2026-06-27T00:37:43.523Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"tool","toolName":"read_files","toolCallId":"mz06q9y0","output":[{"query":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/docs/PHASE_3_INTERACTIVE_TOOLS.md:61-200","result":" 61 | | **Foundry Studio** | Drag-and-drop multi-agent workflow DAG designer, canvas node interaction, cyclical validation checks. | DAG execution engine, Celery task broker synchronization, deployment manifest compiles. |\n 62 | | **Agent Marketplace** | Filterable catalog of pre-configured enterprise agent definitions, installation toggles. | Real-time agent downloads, version control, third-party author portal uploads, licensing, secure keys. |\n 63 | \n 64 | ---\n 65 | \n 66 | ## 3. Phase 4 Target Backend System Architecture\n 67 | \n 68 | To ensure premium execution, the FastAPI backend will utilize a robust architectural stack:\n 69 | \n 70 | 1. **FastAPI Framework (Python 3.12+)**: Leveraging high-performance `asyncio` for scalable multi-connection handling. FastAPI natively exports strict OpenAPI schemas via Redoc or Swagger.\n 71 | 2. **Relational Database (PostgreSQL 16+)**: Managed relational store utilizing SQLAlchemy ORM or SQLModel. Houses user credentials, enterprise workflows, generated proposals, audit histories, and compliance records.\n 72 | 3. **In-Memory Cache (Redis 7+)**: Used for high-speed rate-limiting, short-term OTP validation tokens, and secure JWT blacklist/session states.\n 73 | 4. **AWS S3 or S3-Compatible Object Storage**: Enterprise repository for archiving dynamically compiled PDF blueprints, corporate agreements, custom proposals, and downloadable sandbox snapshots. \n 74 | 5. **No AWS or Cloud Credentials in Phase 3**: In compliance with security policies, all cloud, database, and SMTP services remain abstractly represented via strict, un-hydrated configuration variables.\n 75 | 6. **Authentication Flow**: Completely passwordless, secure, enterprise-tailored One-Time Password (OTP) validation delivered to business emails. Supports corporate domains only, utilizing an abstract communication dispatcher layer (SES, Mailgun, or SendGrid).\n 76 | \n 77 | ---\n 78 | \n 79 | ## 4. FastAPI API Endpoint Catalog\n 80 | \n 81 | This section contains the official HTTP specifications for the target FastAPI endpoints. All endpoints assume a baseline prefix of `/api`. All JSON schemas represent strict Pydantic structures.\n 82 | \n 83 | ---\n 84 | \n 85 | ### 4.1. POST /api/blueprint/generate\n 86 | \n 87 | **Purpose**: Persistently stores and generates an advanced strategic enterprise AI architecture blueprint based on target constraints, compliance frameworks, and infrastructure choices.\n 88 | \n 89 | *   **HTTP Method**: `POST`\n 90 | *   **Path**: `/api/blueprint/generate`\n 91 | *   **Security Requirement**: Optional Session Authentication (registers draft anonymously or links to authenticated user profile).\n 92 | *   **Request Payload Schema (JSON)**:\n 93 |     ```json\n 94 |     {\n 95 |       \"company_name\": \"Acme Global Enterprise\",\n 96 |       \"industry\": \"Financial Services\",\n 97 |       \"compliance_frameworks\": [\"SOC2\", \"HIPAA\", \"EU_AI_ACT\"],\n 98 |       \"data_residency\": \"EU_WEST\",\n 99 |       \"infrastructure_preference\": \"Sovereign_Cloud\",\n100 |       \"deployment_scale\": \"Enterprise_Wide\",\n101 |       \"selected_capabilities\": [\n102 |         \"Knowledge_Graph_Mesh\",\n103 |         \"Autonomous_Agent_Orchestrators\",\n104 |         \"Governance_Guardrails\"\n105 |       ],\n106 |       \"budget_tier\": \"Premium_Enterprise\"\n107 |     }\n108 |     ```\n109 | *   **Response Payload (`[ILLUSTRATIVE MOCK]`)**:\n110 |     ```json\n111 |     {\n112 |       \"blueprint_id\": \"blu_908f7e21-3a0c-4991-88b1-38f7e1b99c72\",\n113 |       \"created_at\": \"2026-06-27T10:30:15Z\",\n114 |       \"compliance_rating\": 98.4,\n115 |       \"estimated_deployment_time_weeks\": 12,\n116 |       \"recommended_architecture_nodes\": [\n117 |         {\n118 |           \"id\": \"node-1\",\n119 |           \"label\": \"GFF AI Sovereign Edge\",\n120 |           \"type\": \"infrastructure\",\n121 |           \"status\": \"critical\"\n122 |         },\n123 |         {\n124 |           \"id\": \"node-2\",\n125 |           \"label\": \"Agent Orchestration Mesh\",\n126 |           \"type\": \"orchestrator\",\n127 |           \"status\": \"active\"\n128 |         }\n129 |       ],\n130 |       \"generated_narrative\": \"Based on financial service constraints, GFF AI prescribes a secure, sovereign-hosted multi-agent cluster backed by real-time governance guardrails.\",\n131 |       \"pdf_download_url\": \"https://assets.gff.ai/blueprints/blu_908f7e21_export.pdf\"\n132 |     }\n133 |     ```\n134 | *   **Error Responses**:\n135 |     *   `400 Bad Request`: If empty inputs or incompatibilities exist in selected frameworks.\n136 |     *   `422 Unprocessable Entity`: Validation failure on Pydantic models (e.g. invalid string enum in `data_residency`).\n137 | \n138 | ---\n139 | \n140 | ### 4.2. POST /api/assessment/score\n141 | \n142 | **Purpose**: Takes complex multi-dimensional AI readiness assessments from the client, calculates overall and categorical readiness scores, and maps out targeted remediation paths.\n143 | \n144 | *   **HTTP Method**: `POST`\n145 | *   **Path**: `/api/assessment/score`\n146 | *   **Security Requirement**: Public / Anonymous Access with optional JWT Session linking.\n147 | *   **Request Payload Schema (JSON)**:\n148 |     ```json\n149 |     {\n150 |       \"assessment_session_id\": \"sess_89a71b3e\",\n151 |       \"answers\": [\n152 |         { \"question_id\": \"data_strategy_01\", \"score\": 4 },\n153 |         { \"question_id\": \"governance_compliance_02\", \"score\": 2 },\n154 |         { \"question_id\": \"infrastructure_cloud_03\", \"score\": 3 },\n155 |         { \"question_id\": \"talent_readiness_04\", \"score\": 5 },\n156 |         { \"question_id\": \"executive_alignment_05\", \"score\": 2 }\n157 |       ],\n158 |       \"organization_size\": \"10000+\",\n159 |       \"comments\": \"Currently migrating core infrastructure to secure air-gapped systems.\"\n160 |     }\n161 |     ```\n162 | *   **Response Payload (`[ILLUSTRATIVE MOCK]`)**:\n163 |     ```json\n164 |     {\n165 |       \"assessment_id\": \"asm_10a29b8c-5521-4f93-90be-8a7199c811fa\",\n166 |       \"calculated_at\": \"2026-06-27T10:32:00Z\",\n167 |       \"overall_readiness_score\": 64.0,\n168 |       \"readiness_tier\": \"Strategic Scale-Up\",\n169 |       \"category_scores\": {\n170 |         \"Data & Strategy\": 80.0,\n171 |         \"Governance & Compliance\": 40.0,\n172 |         \"Infrastructure & Cloud\": 60.0,\n173 |         \"Talent & Enablement\": 100.0,\n174 |         \"Executive Alignment\": 40.0\n175 |       },\n176 |       \"remediation_milestones\": [\n177 |         {\n178 |           \"phase\": \"Phase 1: Compliance Foundation\",\n179 |           \"action\": \"Deploy centralized LLM governance guardrails to address the critical 40% Compliance score.\",\n180 |           \"priority\": \"CRITICAL\"\n181 |         },\n182 |         {\n183 |           \"phase\": \"Phase 2: Strategic Executive Roadmap\",\n184 |           \"action\": \"Establish cross-functional steering committee to align on AI ROI parameters.\",\n185 |           \"priority\": \"HIGH\"\n186 |         }\n187 |       ]\n188 |     }\n189 |     ```\n190 | *   **Error Responses**:\n191 |     *   `400 Bad Request`: Incomplete questionnaire answers (fewer than the required threshold).\n192 | \n193 | ---\n194 | \n195 | ### 4.3. POST /api/roi/calculate\n196 | \n197 | **Purpose**: Processes custom financial variables, staffing costs, and proposed automation volumes to return complete strategic ROI projections, TCO analyses, and amortization timelines.\n198 | \n199 | *   **HTTP Method**: `POST`\n200 | *   **Path**: `/api/roi/calculate`","success":true}],"durationMs"